00:47:17.679 --> 00:47:19.399
for NB Greater as of today.

00:47:19.399 --> 00:47:22.879
That being said, however, you tend to set up NB Greater

00:47:22.879 --> 00:47:25.159
for grading from like Jupyter Notebooks

00:47:25.159 --> 00:47:27.719
should work here as well.

